OL,3,CKrispy Kreme recalls World Cup-
OL,4,Cinspired doughnut over undeclared
OL,5,Callergen
OL,7,FSweet treat chain Krispy Kreme has
OL,8,Frecalled one of its World Cup-inspired
OL,9,Fdoughnuts because it may contain an
OL,10,Fallergen which is not mentioned on the
OL,11,Flabel.
OL,13,FThe brand's Pitch Perfect doughnut,
OL,14,Fwhich is topped with green and white
OL,15,Ficing to look like a football pitch,
OL,16,Fmight contain hazelnuts, making it a
OL,17,Fpossible health risk for anyone with
OL,18,Fan allergy to the nuts, the Food
OL,19,FStandards Agency said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
