FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782125278
OL,3,CKrispy Kreme recalls World Cup-
OL,4,Cinspired doughnut over undeclared
OL,5,Callergen
OL,7,FKrispy Kreme said it was recalling the
OL,8,Fdoughnut, which can be bought
OL,9,Findividually or in a pack of 12 called
OL,10,Fthe Matchday Dozen, on a
OL,11,F"precautionary basis".
OL,13,FIt means customers who bought
OL,14,Findividual Pitch Perfect doughnuts on
OL,15,FFriday or Saturday, or the Matchday
OL,16,FDozen with a best before of Sunday or
OL,17,FMonday, should not eat the item.
