OL,3,CKrispy Kreme recalls World Cup-
OL,4,Cinspired doughnut over undeclared
OL,5,Callergen
OL,7,F"Krispy Kreme takes its
OL,8,Fresponsibilities to consumers
OL,9,Fextremely seriously and always aims to
OL,10,Fensure the highest possible standards
OL,11,Fof product safety," the company said.
OL,13,F"We are sorry for any inconvenience or
OL,14,Fdisappointment this product recall may
OL,15,Fcause you."
OL,17,FAffected customers are asked to
OL,18,Fcontact Krispy Kreme's customer
OL,19,Fservices.
